item.title: My First 10K
item.description: I ran my first 10K race today at the 2015 Panerathon in Youngstown, OH. The following describes how it went. Pro-tip: Don’t eat a full pizza AND Chipotle the night before running a race. Mile 0: Blast off to the bass drop of Calvin Harris’s Sweet Nothing Remix Mile 0 - 1: Pew, pew, pew, I keep passing people. Such slowpokes. This is fun. Clock fastest mile time at 7:34.
